The crew showed another ad earlier in the show for a product liberals could use to relieve their pent-up anger toward President Trump's success.

"The Rage Pillow" plays audio of Trump touting his accomplishments, and can be taken anywhere!

Watch the hilarious ad below, and don't miss the off-the-wall laughs on The Greg Gutfeld Show, Saturday nights at 10:00pm ET on Fox News Channel.

